IntercompanyBillingSettlementHeader is a KeyField

	Representation
		Group Fields
			PayablesCompany
			PayablesCashCode			is a CashCode
			PayablesBankTransactionCode	is a BankTransactionCode
			SettlementID				is AlphaUpper 22

	Ontology
		business class is IntercompanyBillingSettlementHeader
		Context
			IntercompanyBillingGroup

	Patterns
		implements CompactFormat

	Field Rules
		PayablesCompany
			required

			constraint (PayablesCompany.IsValidForIntercompanyBillingSettlement)
				"PayablesCompanyNotSetupForIntercompanyBillingSettlement;ThePayablesCompanyAndItsAssociatedReceivableCompanyMustBeSetupWithDefaultsForIntercompanyBilling"

		PayablesCashCode
			initial value is PayablesCompany.ICBillingDefaultCashCode
			default to PayablesCompany.ICBillingDefaultCashCode
			required
			constraint (PayablesCompanyCashCodeRel exists)	
				"Cash_\CodeIsNotSetUpForThe_\Payables_\Company"	


		PayablesBankTransactionCode
			initial value is PayablesCompany.ICBillingDefaultBankTransactionCode
			default to PayablesCompany.ICBillingDefaultBankTransactionCode
			required

			constraint (!PayablesBankTransactionCode.ManualPaymentNumberReservation)
				"PayableBankTransactionCodeCannotHaveManualPaymentReservationChecked" 	

			constraint (PayablesBankTransactionCode.BankTransactionType.CashPayment)
				"PayableBankTransactionCodeMustBeACashPaymentType"

		SettlementID
			required
			must be numeric
